Their colours and their forms, were then to him}
{\rtlch\ai\ltrch\hich\alang1033\ai\dbch\ai\loch\lang1033\i\par}\pard\plain \s0\sl276\slmult1\ql\widctlpar\hyphpar0\faauto\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\kerning1\strike0\ulc0\cf1\rtlch\af7\afs22\alang1081\ai0\ab0\ltrch\hich\af4\afs22\alang2057\ai0\aulnone\ab0\dbch\af7\langfe2052\loch\f4\fs22\lang2057\i0\ulnone\b0\sl276\slmult1\fi0\li720\lin720\ri0\rin0\brdrt\brdrnone\brdrl\brdrnone\brdrb\brdrnone\brdrr\brdrnone{\rtlch\alang1025\ai\ltrch\hich\alang1033\ai\dbch\langfe1033\loch\lang1033\i
